---
title: PLT (Portobello, Lettuce & Tomato) with Sweet Potato Fries, Tomato-Onion Jam & Basil Aioli
description: You certainly won't miss the "B" in this ultra-satisfying PLT burger. Roasted Portobello adds umami depth, while slow-cooked tomato jam creates the perfect balance of sweet and savory. Looking to make your sweet potato fried extra delicious? Any leftover aioli makes a great dipping sauce (but you didn't hear that from us...)
